---

import Container from "../../Container.astro";
---


<section class="mt-10 delay-[300ms] duration-[600ms] taos:scale-[0.6] taos:opacity-0">
    <Container>

        <div class="w-32 h-32 flex gap-4 rounded-full  shadow-xl bg-gray-800 hover:animate-rotate-y" style="display: block; margin: auto">
            <svg  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  width="24"  height="24"  viewBox="0 -.5 24 22"   fill="none"  stroke="currentColor"  stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round"  stroke-linejoin="round"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-brand-google-big-query w-28 h-28 m-auto text-white "><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M17.73 19.875a2.225 2.225 0 0 1 -1.948 1.125h-7.283a2.222 2.222 0 0 1 -1.947 -1.158l-4.272 -6.75a2.269 2.269 0 0 1 0 -2.184l4.272 -6.75a2.225 2.225 0 0 1 1.946 -1.158h7.285c.809 0 1.554 .443 1.947 1.158l3.98 6.75a2.33 2.33 0 0 1 0 2.25l-3.98 6.75v-.033z" /><path d="M11.5 11.5m-3.5 0a3.5 3.5 0 1 0 7 0a3.5 3.5 0 1 0 -7 0" /><path d="M14 14l2 2" /></svg>

        </div>
        <h1 class=" text-center mt-10  px-4 font-semibold">
            <span class="styleFontH text-3xl md:text-5xl">GESTIÓN DE FACTURAS
        </h1>


        <div class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto text-center lg:py-16 lg:px-6 delay-[300ms] " data-taos-offset="100">
            <figure class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
                <blockquote>
                    <p class="text-1xl sm:text-2xl  md:text-2xl styleFontP text-dark">Las empresas pueden consultar el reporte de las facturas recibidas de cualquier proveedor durante un mes determinado.</p>
    
                    <p class="text-1xl sm:text-2xl md:text-2xl styleFontP text-dark mt-5">Para cada factura puede revisar su último resultado y validación, o volvera a validar.</p>
    
                </blockquote>

            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>
    </Container>
</section>


<style>
    .styleFontH{
        font-family: "Saira", sans-serif ;
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .styleFontP{
        font-family: "Saira", sans-serif ;
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 100;
    }
</style>